Added code-golfed evilness tester

A number is evil if its binary representation has an even amount of 1s.
```
0 = 0     --> 1
2 = 10   --> 0
3 = 11  --> 1
5 = 101   --> 1
11 = 1011  --> 0
29 = 11101 --> 1
```
